# Helm Chart Conventions

- Charts live in `apps/{app-name}/` with `Chart.yaml`, `values.yaml`, `templates/`
- All deployments must include health probes (readinessProbe, livenessProbe)
- Set resource requests and limits on every container
- Use `ExternalSecret` resources (not manual K8s Secrets) for sensitive values
- `ExternalSecret` references `ClusterSecretStore` named `azure-key-vault`
- PVCs should use `azure-files-csi` or `azure-blob-csi` storage classes
- Use `{{ .Release.Name }}` prefix for resource names
